snippet.title: Amber Heard | Beautiful
snippet.description:
Dedicated to Ivy ('cause she's an amazing friend, I'm so lucky to know her. Love ya, babeh)
So hey guys (:
Long time no see, I know. But I've been busy with school & all : (, sorry. But I finally managed to finish this video, I'm soo happy! *hh* Love Amber! She's amazing, gorgeous and so talented. + this song is just wonderful. Hope you like this vid., it didn't turn out so good, but still :p Hope you enjoyed it. BTW lovexdealer is my back-up account (: 

CREDITS:
Fandom: Amber Heard
Song: Beautiful
Artist: Patrick Nuo
